        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-111",
        "content": "A piece of wreckage is thrown upon the beach, and you wonder what dire disaster happened far out at sea, and if the rest of the ship went to the bottom with all on board.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
