        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/111/126265/111_126265_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-111",
        "content": "But fortune favored us, and the much desired picture was secured.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-111_126265_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/111/126265/111_126265_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-111",
        "content": "Far out the lighthouse stands anchored to the rocks, the waves dashing against it, as if to tear it from its firm foundation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-111_126265_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/111/126265/111_126265_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-111",
        "content": "But it defies them all, and sends the cheery beacon light over the waters, to guide the stately ships between the portals of the Golden Gate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
